summary:
Cosmo Online Store (trading as 'My Store') is an e-commerce dropshipping business operating on the Shopify platform. The company sells a diverse range of consumer products across multiple categories including home and kitchen items, pet supplies, sports and fitness equipment, toys, and baby products. All products are listed as 'Sold out' on the website, suggesting the store may be in a setup or maintenance phase.

The business operates as a dropshipping model, shipping products directly from international suppliers to customers worldwide. They offer free shipping to the UK and most countries, with estimated delivery times ranging from 7-30 business days depending on the region. The company has a 30-day return policy and provides standard e-commerce policies including privacy policy, terms of service, and shipping policy.

The store appears to be based in Pakistan with a US contact address listed in their privacy policy. They use a single email address (info.madiioutreach@gmail.com) for all customer communications including orders, returns, and general inquiries. The website follows standard e-commerce practices with product listings, shopping cart functionality, and policy pages, though all products are currently marked as unavailable.
